<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV57">
<l>caṅkutaṅku muṉkainaṅkai koṅkaitaṅka luṟṟavaṉ</l>
<l>aṅkamaṅka vaṉṟuceṉṟa ṭartteṟinta vāḻiyāṉ</l>
<l>koṅkutaṅku vārkuḻalma ṭantaimārku ṭaintanīr</l>
<l>poṅkutaṇku ṭantaiyuḷki ṭantapuṇṭa rīkaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The ocean[-bodied Rāma]—who went [to Laṅkā], attacked and destroyed</l>
<l>[Rāvaṇa] who desired to stay on the breasts of the lady (Sītā) with braceleted hands</l>
<l rend="indent">so that his limbs perished—</l>
<l>is the lotus[-eyed Lord] who reclined inside the cool Kuṭantai</l>
<l>with abundant water[bodies] in which women with long, fragrant locks bathe!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
